Thank you Peter, =0A=0AI amended the widget slightly. With this version the=
 searched pattern is shown again when you search-forward beyond the first m=
atch. As far as I can tell that is how history works in Matlab and Fish. =
=0A=0AAttached for users who also like this behavior. =0A=0ABest wishes, =
=0A=0AGuido =0A=0A--- On Fri, 10/2/09, Peter Stephenson <pws@csr.com> wrote=
